org.apache.oozie.local
Class LocalOozie

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.oozie.local.LocalOozie

public class LocalOozie
extends Object

LocalOozie runs workflows in an embedded Oozie instance .

LocalOozie is meant for development/debugging purposes only.
